column5:
Rexulti is an anti-psychotic, so be wary of that before starting a new medication. It is not an antidepressant. But, it can help with depression. Keep in mind that they bring new side effects compared to antidepressants. 

&#x200B;

I haven't taken it personally, because I found a med that worked for me before I tried it. But from what I hear it's an excellent drug.
